name: Dance #4 (Bedhaya Sapta)
description: The Bedhaya Sapta dance was created by Sri Sultan Hamengku Buwono IX in 1943. The idea for the story came when he got the book Babad Pasundhan which contains the story of two courtiers of Sultan Agung, namely Prince Nampabaya and Prince Lirbaya. To find out more stories from this dance. you can search on the internet with the keyword "Bedhaya Sapta Dance"
